import random
def row_strategy(history):
    if not history:
        return 0
    # Randomly switch every 3 rounds to break the copying pattern
    # This prevents opponent from exploiting our move history.
    round_num = len(history)
    if round_num % 3 == 0:
        return 1 - history[-1][0]
    return history[-1][0]
ENDOFFILE
